        "title": "Split diffs Shiki language pack",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Split the diffs viewer Shiki runtime into a curated default bundle plus an optional `diffs-language-pack` plugin for extended languages.\n- Keep common languages highlighted out of the box and degrade uncommon language hints to plain text unless the language pack is available.\n- Add language-pack plugin assets, package metadata, docs, generated plugin inventory/reference docs, and targeted tests for language selection and asset serving.\n\n## Bundle size metrics\n\nMeasured with `node` using raw byte length, `zlib.gzipSync(..., { level: 9 })`, and `zlib.brotliCompressSync(..., { BROTLI_PARAM_QUALITY: 11 })` after rebuilding both viewer runtimes.\n\n| Runtime | Raw bytes | gzip bytes | brotli bytes |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| Previous/full language runtime (`extensions/diffs-language-pack/assets/viewer-runtime.js`) | 9,899,800 | 1,726,566 | 1,130,593 |\n| New default diffs runtime (`extensions/diffs/assets/viewer-runtime.js`) | 4,479,969 | 733,971 | 464,667 |\n| Default bundle reduction | 5,419,831 | 992,595 | 665,926 |\n| Default bundle reduction percent | 54.75% | 57.49% | 58.90% |\n\n## Verification\n\n- `bun scripts/build-viewer.mjs` in `extensions/diffs`\n- `bun scripts/build-viewer.mjs` in `extensions/diffs-language-pack`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/diffs/src/language-hints.test.ts extensions/diffs/src/render.test.ts extensions/diffs/src/config.test.ts extensions/diffs/src/store.test.ts extensions/diffs/src/browser.test.ts` (84 tests passed)\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/bundled-plugin-assets.test.ts test/plugin-npm-release.test.ts test/plugin-npm-package-manifest.test.ts` (36 tests passed)\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.extensions.json extensions/diffs/api.ts extensions/diffs/index.ts extensions/diffs/runtime-api.ts extensions/diffs/src extensions/diffs/scripts extensions/diffs-language-pack/api.ts extensions/diffs-language-pack/index.ts extensions/diffs-language-pack/src extensions/diffs-language-pack/scripts`\n- `node scripts/generate-plugin-inventory-doc.mjs --check`\n- `git diff --check`\n- Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01kskvvv5vfrvcsea50cz6p8qd`, Actions run https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/actions/runs/26491235650: in progress at PR creation for `corepack pnpm check:changed` followed by `corepack pnpm build`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: default diffs viewer no longer ships the full Shiki language runtime; uncommon languages use the optional `diffs-language-pack` runtime when that plugin is available.\n\nReal environment tested: local Codex worktree on macOS with Node/Bun repo wrappers; Testbox-through-Crabbox Linux proof started.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: see Verification.\n\nEvidence after fix: targeted diffs language/render/asset tests and plugin package/static asset contract tests passed; both viewer runtimes rebuilt and measured.\n\nObserved result after fix: common languages stay in the default runtime, uncommon language hints fall back to text without the language pack, and the language-pack viewer asset is selected when available.\n\nWhat was not tested: remote Testbox changed check/build was still running when this PR was opened.\n",
